Package: rjsimplegame
Type: Package
Title: Simple Javascript game in R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Stathis", "Grigoropoulos", email = "grstathis@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Stathis Grigoropoulos <stathis.grigoropoulos@nl.ey.com>
Description: Port of the simple game written in Javascript at the w3.schools.com.
  Use the arrows of the keyboard to move the red square and avoid the obstacles.
  Visit https://www.w3schools.com/graphics/game_controllers.asp.
  The purpose of the package is to showcase the possibilites of the htmlwidgets package. 
License: MIT License.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.1)
Imports:
    htmlwidgets,
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
